Whip 2D Toolkit
[DWF Toolkit Components]

Collaboration diagram for Whip 2D Toolkit:

This module is the streaming I/O layer for Whip 2D vector graphics. It has been provide by Autodesk for Whip and DWF users since 1996. The API, specification and additional documentation provided as part of the DWF Toolkit distribution.
